name: Shoot Up: Reach the End !
description:
Tough levels; don’t last. You never know how difficult each level is. But many won’t allow you to pass without testing your gaming skill.
Move the firing jet to clear the path and score more.
Shoot accurately on numbered blocks and push smartly on the unnumbered blocks.
Use multi bullets and heavy bullet power-ups effectively.
Upgrades accelerate the experience and powers opportunity to score more.
Challenge your friends to cross the level you crossed; many cannot do.

Game Features:
- Free to play
- A single flight to fire and move obstacles
- OMG experience when you cross certain levels
- One and only game where you could shoot and push to rise your parachute
